Why then should Sluttery poyson any Man's Stomach, seeing Venus her self was born out of the Scum of the Sea? And it hath been observ'd how for the most part the rarest and most excellent Men for Learning, Wit and Sence have been most negligent and careless in their Apparel;
and as we say Slovens: Erasmus saith of Sir Thomas Moore, Quod à puero semper in vestitu fuit negligen
